      "text": "why would you wanna put\nup with listening to me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 17814.0,
      "end_time": 20879.0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, grammar\nis a set of conventions"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 20879.0,
      "end_time": 23600.0,
      "text": "and rules that govern language."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 23600.0,
      "end_time": 26572.0,
      "text": "So what's the difference\nbetween a convention and a rule?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 26572.0,
      "end_time": 30751.0,
      "text": "Well, a rule is kind of\nthe bare minimum of what"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 30751.0,
      "end_time": 33050.0,
      "text": "it takes to make your\nlanguage understandable"
