    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 33050.0,
      "end_time": 34513.0,
      "text": "by other people, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 34513.0,
      "end_time": 37299.0,
      "text": "So in order to make a\ncar work, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 37299.0,
      "end_time": 39691.0,
      "text": "in order to make it move\nforward as intended,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 39691.0,
      "end_time": 42895.0,
      "text": "the wheels have to go on the\nbottom instead of the roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 42895.0,
      "end_time": 44730.0,
      "text": "That's a rule."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 44730.0,
      "end_time": 48004.0,
      "text": "The idea that all cars should\nbe painted teal, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 48004.0,
      "end_time": 50001.0,
      "text": "is a convention."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 50001.0,
      "end_time": 52950.0,
      "text": "Now is that true that\nall cars should be teal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 52950.0,
      "end_time": 55829.0,
      "text": "No, not necessarily, but that\nleads me to my second point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 55829.0,
      "end_time": 58639.0,
      "text": "that grammar is context dependent."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 58639.0,
      "end_time": 59892.0,
      "text": "The kind of grammar that you use"
